  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Amend KRS 64.5277 to define \"excess credit hours\"; amend KRS 64.5278 to allow a city to establish different base incentive amounts for different types of city officers by ordinance; remove minimum and maximum payment amounts."
